{"tid":2241998,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英格蘭足總消息指，英超Big 6球會威脅如果Project Big Picture不獲通過，將退出英超聯賽","createTime":"2020-10-13T16:46:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T08:04:58.000Z","uid":2169,"like":7,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"fe9b52bbdc8db061a009086cff09ec7b98da0cbb","tid":2241998,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:46:53.000Z","msg":"【#體嘢突發】<br />\n<br />\n《Telegraph》記者Ben Rumsby引述英格蘭足總消息指，英超Big 6球會威脅如果Project Big Picture不獲通過，將退出英超聯賽。<br />\n<br />\n該改革方案最富爭議之處，是廢除現有投票制度（20球會中有14家贊成票，便能通過方案），並賦予9家「長期持份者」球會有超然地位，包括Big 6以及修咸頓、韋斯咸、愛華頓。如果以後9支球隊之中有6票贊成，就可以改動任何重要政策，包括修訂球例、簽訂合約、人事任免、球會擁有權變更、改變電視轉播或贊助合約的資金分配等。英國媒體披露，該計劃獲得曼聯及利物浦大力支持。<br />\n<br />\n#利物浦 球迷團體Spirit of Shankly表明反對。<br />\n<br />\n#體嘢 #sportsyeah"},{"pid":"de1ab0f9f706dcb9e84454220e332bc188e27598","tid":2241998,"uid":73381,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:48:29.000Z","msg":"韋斯咸隊垃圾都有份我哋壯卡素冇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c83eac9e4a56833c39ac9d171d4801ed3b7c13","tid":2241998,"uid":2169,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"de1ab0f9f706dcb9e84454220e332bc188e27598","tid":2241998,"uid":73381,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:48:29.000Z","msg":"韋斯咸隊垃圾都有份我哋壯卡素冇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:49:24.000Z","msg":"你地得頓哥一條友carry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"487e05bd22708ce3ab7f37a0b0bd304e14b0bab6","tid":2241998,"uid":20563,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:51:05.000Z","msg":"英超聯合國？玩安理會常任理事國投票？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9df8c36219e51adf627bdcd4ed0fc5dc01f6f44","tid":2241998,"uid":82938,"like":19,"dislike